sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as FastAPI Application
    participant Context as Context Retrieval Plugin
    participant Embedding as Embedding Service
    participant Search as Azure AI Search
    participant LLM as Language Model
    participant Cost as Cost Tracker
    
    Note over User,Cost: Content Generation with Context
    
    User->>App: Request content generation
    App->>Context: retrieve_context_context(query, context_type)
    
    Note over Context: Context Retrieval Phase
    Context->>Embedding: generate_embeddings([query])
    Embedding->>Embedding: Create query vector
    Embedding-->>Context: Query embedding vector
    
    Context->>Search: context_search(embedding, top_k=3)
    Search->>Search: Semantic similarity search
    Search-->>Context: Relevant documents with scores
    
    Context->>Context: Filter by relevance threshold (0.7)
    Context->>Context: Format context for prompt
    
    Note over Context: Content Generation Phase
    Context->>LLM: generate_with_context(prompt + context)
    LLM->>LLM: Process enhanced prompt
    LLM-->>Context: Generated content
    
    Context->>Cost: log_ai_call(usage, model_config)
    Cost->>Cost: Calculate cost and update balance
    
    Context-->>App: Enhanced response with context
    App-->>User: Final generated content
    
    Note over User,Cost: Document Indexing Flow
    
    User->>App: Upload document
    App->>App: Process and chunk document
    App->>Embedding: generate_embeddings(chunks)
    Embedding-->>App: Chunk embeddings
    App->>Search: upload_documents(chunks + embeddings)
    Search-->>App: Indexing confirmation
    App-->>User: Upload complete
